OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBecoming
OL,6,Fcloudy overnight as low cloud and mist
OL,7,Fdevelops in the east of the region
OL,8,Fperhaps spreading westwards. Winds
OL,9,Fremain light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FWednesday sees low cloud
OL,12,Fand mist lifting and clearing during
OL,13,Fthe morning, with some long brighter
OL,14,Fspells developing for the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,17,Fspells expected Thursday before
OL,18,Fevening rain. Rain clears Friday
OL,19,Fmorning, leaving further sunny spells.
OL,20,FSaturday turns cloudy with rain and
OL,21,Fdrizzle.
